
paye [options] [package] ...

 <options>      <package>    <job>
 cl                                                 Clear the cache
 upak           app.pa                              Unpack 'app.pa' archive package
 pak            app                                 Build 'app' project
 in             app                                 Install 'app' package
 rm             app                                 Remove 'app' package
 add            https://example.com/app.pa          Add 'app' mirror
 del            app                                 Remove 'app' mirror
 info           app                                 Show informations about 'app'
 get            app                                 Download 'app' archive package
 git            https://github.com/example/app      Install 'app' from git
 ls                                                 List all installed packages
 up                                                 Update cloud software
 crt            app                                 Create 'app' project